snippet.title: OFFICIAL TRAILER | You're a N64 taxi and there's 🚫 no jump button?
snippet.description:
🚕 OUT NOW! 👉 http://taxi.game

Yellow Taxi Goes Vroom is a love letter to the N64 era of collectathons, but you’re a yellow taxi and there’s no jump button!
